content.name: Kaws BFF Plush Black
content.description: Originally released at the "Where The End Starts" exhibit in Fort Worth, Texas, the Black BFF Plush was one of the most sought after KAWS products in recent memory. After a hyped initial release, the plush would go on to release on KAWSONE just a few months later, crashing the website as ten of thousands of users scrambled for just a few available plushes. The figure comes in a custom box with a removable lid, and features elements of KAWS' classic companion character. Each plush is sequentially numbered to 3000

content.name: Kaws Stormtrooper
content.description:
Fan-favorite character Stormtrooper is the latest subject to receive a KAWS Companion makeover courtesy of Medicom Toy and OriginalFake.

Fun reimagining of the evil Star Wars empire’s patrol unit. The white Storm Trooper created in 2008 has dimensions 10 IN / 25.4 CM. The KAWS signature Inflated skull literally pops out of the Companion’s helmet, while the brand’s iconic xxs are positioned over the eyes. 12
